{"tid":487966,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【認真討論】在香港，遊行示威仲有作用咩？","createTime":"2017-12-03T09:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T10:57:52.000Z","uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7736dd982d25d50f3deff9c07fb9687be026a8cf","tid":487966,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T09:03:28.000Z","msg":"古語有云：「裝睡的人叫不醒。」遊行示威，就是假定當權者太離地，聽不到國民既聲音。國民通過沿途大叫口號，叫醒政府，要佢地回應訴求，同做野。<br />\n<br />\n香港社會種種問題，係立法會、佔中、過去十年大大小小和平既激烈既遊行示威，反反覆覆講到口都臭。政府官員又點會唔知？知而不改，只得兩個原因：不為 or 不能。<br />\n<br />\n97主權移交初期，為左保存一國兩制呢個示範單位畀台灣同國際社會睇，市民反對既聲音，中共同香港政府都仲有回應下。可惜，自從中國富起來，習近平上場，對香港政策就係順我者昌、逆我者亡、無得商量。你睇到既係一眾香港官員只識得跟隨中共指令，不能偏離。另一方面，因為缺乏真正既普選，佢地既政治前途唔係掌握係市民手上，所前前幾年搞到佔中都好，佢地都無需對反對意見作出任何妥協。你叫得幾多人出黎、叫得幾大聲都好，佢睬你都有味！<br />\n<br />\n有此背景，我想請問年年事無大小都搞遊行既搞手、叫人出黎上街既政客，今時今日，就算帶埋個細路出黎行，還有作用嗎？<br />\n<br />\n係終點站宣佈「畀D掌聲自己」「呢個係階段性勝利」之後，你地得到捐款，咁我地得到D咩呢又？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同步連載，岩睇既請like and share：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/WestRiceGoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWestRiceGoo&d=I36YCanTEP2dIDNXEpB7I4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=58441c8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/WestRiceGoo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/westricegoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fwestricegoo&d=I36YCanTEP2dIDNXEpB7I4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=8d5f1591\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.instagram.com/westricegoo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/03/170323_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F03%2F170323_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d45b2e07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a512c3d45c2d4dd89a3ca0e6aa2a68630e1f6c1","tid":487966,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd238d2b0c600ef7bafa5944f0c95bf9718bc0a","tid":487966,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:33:16.000Z","msg":"遊行示威有用<br />\n但大前提係搞手唔可以講自己會和平進行"},{"pid":"5b6b1706fe86e55b0f9efe8e899bc87e2545db73","tid":487966,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:38:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遊行示威有用<br />\n但大前提係搞手唔可以講自己會和平進行</blockquote><br />\n但而家99%既遊行都係和理非非嘉年華style"},{"pid":"647a9069cb30b6397005e7d9b7d8d836d3b3d020","tid":487966,"uid":160094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:43:15.000Z","msg":"對政府冇用<br />\n都係俾政黨籌下錢cap下水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8237a68f0b6ddc828851ab97b5f80413129b55cd","tid":487966,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:53:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66da0aba3847c733c873a8e73c58d72a4d42903d","tid":487966,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:55:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對政府冇用<br />\n都係俾政黨籌下錢cap下水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔撚明點解仲有人捐錢"},{"pid":"697a7002d928c5e0fe9214f59e68f4c9fc2e70e7","tid":487966,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:57:52.000Z","msg":"討論還討論<br />\n點解又要貼FB IG<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}